<paragraph blockId="62.[151,1436,1538,1966]" pageId="62" pageNumber="63">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,368,1686,1711]" pageId="62" pageNumber="63">Identification.</emphasis>
Test heart-shaped; lacking tubercles in ambulacrum outside petals, small primary tubercles rarely found towards ambitus in anterior ambulacra, no tubercles in posterior ambulacra; spines short; purple in color.
